
Install instructions for sh-0.0.x
---------------------------------

1. Type `make'

To install sh

Type `make install'.  To install the sh program into the /bin directory
INSTALL_DIR needs to be set to root directory, /.  

INSTALL_DIR=/
sh will be in /bin, and man pages in /usr/man

This is really the only settings for INSTALL_DIR unless you have a test
partition mounted on the filesystem,

INSTALL_DIR=/plural/

sh will be in /plural/bin, and man pages in /plural/usr/man
